&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cv up to 0.9, body only 16mm wide&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Long life up to 200 million cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Base mounted for ease of repair&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;One screw for electrical and air connection of valves&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple manifolds and electrical connections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Built-in one-touch fittings (metric &amp; inch)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

